# ============================================================================
# AUTONOMOUS MODE COMMANDS
# ============================================================================

# Activation commands (any triggers autonomous mode):
# /autonomous, /turbo, /fullaccess, /godmode, /letitwork

# When activated:
# - Grant FULL_ACCESS permissions
# - Duration: 30 minutes (auto-disable)
# - Still show all actions (transparency ON)
# - Auto-save every 10 operations
# - Emergency stop: /stop, /halt, /emergency

# Deactivation commands:
# /stop, /autonomous off, /normal, /safe

# Status check:
# /autonomous status - Show current mode and stats

# Recovery:
# /restore - Rollback to auto-save snapshot
# /rollback - Git rollback
# /undo - Undo last operation

# ============================================================================
